	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I completed this quest today, with two people. Took us about 8 hrs. L23 Pally and L32 druid. I (the druid) made about 3 yellow bubs in the process. To summarise, you can collect all the pieces you need, then go and do the quest. Each NPC gives you a token which needs to be given to the next NPC. I doubt any of the steps can be avoided. Just in case you're having trouble with any of the NPC, I had to have them targetted for the final phrase or they would not give me the token.<BR>
<BR>
To summarise the mobs:<BR>
Crazed Goblin in Butcher drops a blade<BR>
Crazed Ghoul in Unrest drops a heart<BR>
Crazed Goblin in HighKeep drops a scroll<BR>
&quot;Skeleton&quot; in Najenna drops a hilt.<BR>
<BR>
Note that all the mobs that drop the bits are around level 28 or so. If your mob is not 28 or so, it's the wrong mob :)<BR>
<BR>
NPC's will despawn as you get the token so if you're doing it with several people at a time, just hang around for 5 mins and they will repop in the same place.<BR>
<BR>
The final npc in Lavastorm gives you the bag. Put the 4 items in the bag, combine and presto! One Ghoulbane!<BR>
<BR>
Unless it contradicts what I've just written, the information on the process and npc locs provided by the previous posters was correct.<BR>
<BR>
Have fun Questing!<BR>
Sorcha<BR>
<BR>
PS, Ghoulbane was worth 1kpp on Prexus before the May30 patch. I expect it will be almost worthless in a week due to this quest. /shrug
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
